{"tid":1283740,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"個個都我冇野講，咁下一步係點？","createTime":"2019-07-04T01:52:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T03:15:00.000Z","uid":57840,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"febe1256a4b07105d3998d1a44d18524290abc71","tid":1283740,"uid":57840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:52:39.000Z","msg":"七一立法會，好多義士有機會被捕。大家焦點都去晒會唔會俾警察拉，大部分post都係講應對狗隻多。<br />\n<br />\n但大家唔好忘記，訴求都仲係未有回應。我明白大家都好攰，同埋覺得做乜都冇用。但其實國際已經眾焦係香港，香港人唔可以咩都停底，被警方拉起底組行動牽住走。<br />\n勇武可能要再審慎評估局勢，<br />\n但我覺得和理非行動唔可以停。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家點睇"},{"pid":"7b175e81451590323e12b2b81de979fd6a914e82","tid":1283740,"uid":57840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:53:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ef28b7dc2f81c2904755d235e5dae0e48d1b76c9","tid":1283740,"uid":20769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"6/7 光復屯門<br />\n7/7 九龍區大遊行"},{"pid":"691f9e38b28e23e43c1a215a480fca1524fd904f","tid":1283740,"uid":57840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ef28b7dc2f81c2904755d235e5dae0e48d1b76c9","tid":1283740,"uid":20769,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T01:54:46.000Z","msg":"6/7 光復屯門<br />\n7/7 九龍區大遊行"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:03:39.000Z","msg":"收到，我會睇下。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f754b9532ea6fc3343906c0a244f539c5daa889","tid":1283740,"uid":108337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"休息完要繼續努力 不鬆懈"},{"pid":"fb0d4d1ee38c249ada303871d470509d9ef38a44","tid":1283740,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T02:05:43.000Z","msg":"要求釋放，佢就拉多啲"},{"pid":"1d5667ef8f2dc217987e5ca1d02f1242522d323e","tid":1283740,"uid":57840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fb0d4d1ee38c249ada303871d470509d9ef38a44","tid":1283740,"uid":173326,"like":0,"